Package: aria-man-pages
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: aria-compiler
Description: Manual pages for the Aria programming language
 This package contains comprehensive manual pages for the Aria programming
 language, covering:
  - Type system (int32, string, arrays, structs, etc.)
  - Functions (async, sync, closures, etc.)
  - Control flow (if, match, loops, etc.)
  - Memory management (GC, ownership, borrowing)
  - Standard library functions
  - Module system
  - Advanced features
 .
 The manual pages are organized by category and fully cross-referenced.
 Use 'man aria' for the main index or 'apropos aria' to search topics.
